{"tid":1834162,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「緊急」香港出現首宗武漢野味肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-22T09:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:28:48.000Z","uid":96970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce21a1bb4b58df39c477bbb49ce2a95f1c81ef0f","tid":1834162,"uid":96970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢肺炎疫情大爆發並擴散至多個地區，香港終告失守！消息指，香港今日(22日)確診首宗武漢肺炎感染病例。患者目前在伊利沙伯醫院隔離治療，正等候第二次測試覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，患者為一名內地男旅客，昨晚(21日)經高鐵抵達香港時被發現有發燒徵狀，他亦報稱曾到過武漢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200122/mobile/bkn-20200122170259493-0122_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200122%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200122170259493-0122_00822_001.html&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=013505c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200122/mobile/bkn-20200122170259493-0122_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"93c5200ead0fb8c0e38bf5ca7e4af1dc972082ec","tid":1834162,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/jj9Z3v0V/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fjj9Z3v0V%2Fimage.png&h=d3427986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/827284/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_180923/20180923_e23e0b8afe24867f847cXhgV9XsBCeDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F827284%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_180923%2F20180923_e23e0b8afe24867f847cXhgV9XsBCeDo.jpg&h=39261390&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e446c636da57d252b4efba973eb9801f02f2b78","tid":1834162,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8Dibcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A